replies.body:
Hi imryaan!

Happy Birthday!
I have seen you quite a lot in game.
I will rank you 9.5/10 for PVP.
How do you PvP so well?? You should teach me sometime. :)
You are an awesome person. xD
Anyways..let's go to the questions!

1. How old are you right now?
2. How tall are you?
3. Who is your favorite moderator?
4. What country do you live in?
5. What are your opinions on me?
6. What are your opinions on South Korea and Greece?
7. How many languages can you speak?
8. If you can go anywhere for 7 days, where would you go?
9. What is your favorite food?
10. What is your favorite dessert?

Ok. That's it.
I was going to ask more, but I will let you off the hook, so that you can celebrate your birthday xD
Even though I can't go on TeamSpeak often, I will try to be there, one day.
Please continue to be a kind person, like you are right now.
And I hope to see you in game!
Bye!
